info.name: Elise-chan
info.description: The fourth edition of the Elise-chan Bot series, featuring updated functionality, economy, and music. This edition is the transition period of the Elise-chan Bot from traditional commands to slash commands. Began developing on October 29, 2023, and released on December 25, 2023. This version enforces a better command structure, utilizing the newest Elise-chan API 'ECA-3' version.
funFacts: The bot was originally written in pure Discord.JS but had to be rewritten to a "newbie" library because the developer is having hard time writing music commands!
